Usage: create_clock [-help] [<sources>] [-add] [-comment <string>]
                    [-name <clock_name>] -period <period_value>
                    [-waveform <edge_list>]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
<sources>                  # List of pins or ports associated with the clock
                           # (string, optional)
-add                       # Multiple clocks on the same source
                           # (bool, optional)
-comment <string>          # Not supported option (string, optional)
-name <clock_name>         # String name of the clock (string, optional)
-period <period_value>     # Clock period in library time units
                           # (float, required)
-waveform <edge_list>      # Rise and fall edge times of the clock
                           # (string, optional)